&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stripe is seeking an AEO &amp;amp; GEO Marketing Manager to lead the channel. This individual will play a critical role in growing new user acquisition from platforms including ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI Overviews / AI Mode. The scope of the role includes Generative Engine Optimization (GEO), also known as Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) or LLM Search Optimization (LLMO), improving agent experience, and integrating AI capabilities to improve the performance and efficiency of SEO and AEO channels.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This individual will spearhead efforts by developing and executing a roadmap of activities and experiments to improve AEO performance. They will have the opportunity to work closely with cross-functional partners including Growth Marketing, Content Marketing, Engineering, and Analytics at Stripe.&lt;/p&gt;
