&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Pricing Strategy team is part of Stripe&#39;s Product Marketing organization and is responsible for how Stripe prices its products. Our work is highly cross-functional and we partner closely with Product, Finance, and Sales to tackle some of Stripe&#39;s most visible and commercially impactful decisions. We&#39;re looking for someone who can blend financial analysis, strategic thinking, and stakeholder engagement to help us price new products and evaluate their pricing performance as the products evolve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
