&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be a pragmatic problem-solver. &lt;/strong&gt;You are comfortable making and defending well-reasoned judgments even when data is imperfect or incomplete, and know how to ask the right questions and find creative analytical approaches to move forward with confidence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be a collaborator&lt;/strong&gt;. You partner effectively across Engineering, Product, Finance, and Sales to drive alignment and get things built&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
