&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability of defining &amp;amp; driving complex initiatives/projects across multiple teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proven success with cross-discipline and cross-team collaborations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
