&lt;li&gt;A strategist and scaler, who can connect the dots between where we’re going and how we need to nudge the organization to get there&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A partner and connector who builds trusted relationships with managers and leaders by providing deep insights and helping them see around corners&lt;/li&gt;
