&lt;p&gt;As a Product Lead on the Payments Intelligence team, you’ll be responsible for scoping, designing, and building intuitive features that help users maximize their revenue while minimizing their cost while shaping our intelligence platform. You will partner with many functions at Stripe, with the opportunity to both work on infrastructure/platform systems, as well as produce direct user-facing business impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Day to day you’ll be working closely with a team of engineers and data scientists. You’ll collaborate with peers in Design, Product Marketing, Partnerships and many others to craft the vision for our Payments Intelligence products.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
