&lt;li&gt;Work closely with other Stripe teams to improve our product offerings and messaging around new products and features&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain unique insights into how thousands of businesses on Stripe scale and operate&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have an opportunity to learn how Stripe operates from ground up and make a real impact on the future on organization&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with global operations specialists or business process owners to run a critical workflow&lt;/li&gt;
