&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conceptualize and execute risk strategies for Stripe’s rapidly growing merchant portfolio by harnessing deep subject matter expertise in risk management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage SQL skills to drive quantitative analysis and data visualizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quantify the impact to Stripe’s direct profit and losses for each recommended strategy&lt;/li&gt;
