&lt;li&gt;Must have a Bachelor&#39;s degree or foreign equivalent in Business Administration, Economics, Information Systems, or a related field, plus 5 years of post-bachelor’s, progressive related experience in a Financial Risk Specialist or related occupation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 years of experience working with, aggregating, and running analysis on large data sets, including utilizing SQL and common BI tools (e.g. Tableau)&lt;/li&gt;
