&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;8+ years of relevant experience, with 3+ years of people management experience preferred&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
