&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to build relationships with strategic client and industry thought leaders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to understand and articulate technical concepts, and translate them into industry- or business-relevant terms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
