&lt;li&gt;Create and manage operational processes such as portfolio design, target setting and headcount strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales leadership and cross-functional teams to manage forecasting, translate business needs into actionable operational plans, and identify risks and opportunities to support strategic decision making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own core rhythm-of-business processes, including weekly forecasting, monthly/quarterly business reviews, and OKR tracking, ensuring visibility, accountability, and alignment against business priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute initiatives designed to optimize sales team efficiency and productivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive rhythm of business with strong operational rigor.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide insights on key performance metrics and priorities (e.g. weekly, monthly, quarterly business reviews), identify key roadblocks to progress, and work efficiently to remove them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide business analytic strength to help drive initiatives critical to ongoing growth and provide key insights for business leadership to support strategic decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive local / regional critical projects and initiatives and drive alignment with cross-functional teams across the organization by developing detailed project plans with activity based milestones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee implementation of enabling systems and tools, working closely with internal systems teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
