&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview:&lt;/strong&gt; Bridge Building S.A. (BBSA) is building a Luxembourg-regulated EMI and CASP. We are seeking a Treasury Manager to build and operate BBSA’s capital, liquidity, and treasury management framework, including liquidity forecasting, banking operations, counterparty risk oversight, and governance reporting. The role partners closely with Finance, Safeguarding, Risk, and Compliance to ensure strong controls, resilience, and inspection-ready documentation.&lt;/p&gt;
